Package net.opentsdb.query.filter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TagVFilter
    A base class for tag value filters that may execute against rows that come out of a scanner to determine if we should include them in the results or not.
    TagVFilter.Builder
    Builder class used for deserializing filters from JSON queries via Jackson since we don't want the user to worry about the class name.
    TagVLiteralOrFilter
    A filter that lets the user list one or more explicit strings that should be included in a result set for aggregation.
    TagVLiteralOrFilter.TagVILiteralOrFilter
    Case insensitive version
    TagVNotKeyFilter  
    TagVNotLiteralOrFilter
    A filter that lets the user list one or more explicit strings that should NOT be included in a result set for aggregation.
    TagVNotLiteralOrFilter.TagVNotILiteralOrFilter
    Case insensitive version
    TagVRegexFilter
    A filter that allows for regular expression matching on tag values.
    TagVWildcardFilter
    Performs basic wild card searching.
    TagVWildcardFilter.TagVIWildcardFilter
    Case insensitive version
